For all Proactive Disclosure searches (contracts, gratns, travel, etc.) enable the ability for
clients to search by department names or acronyms. For example, a searcher could clickt the 
"Canada Revenue Agency" facet on the left-side OR they could type the name into the text search box.

Similarly, uses can also search by current department acronyms like "RCMP" or old acronyms like "PWGSC".
Englisn and French acronyms are supported.

